body_html:
@meghna1301: I can reproduce your problem with master branch. I don't know what happened. I guess some changes to TF Lite runtime (after I created this issue) broke files converted by old TOCO (well, even converting with TOCO from master branch has the same dimension problem). Something must be wrong. You should create another issue I think.

@aselle @rmlarsen FYI, I am not sure if this is problem of tensorflow/contrib/lite/kernels/concatenation.cc, I saw your names in the commit log of concatenation.cc
